Architecture: any
Provides: ufoai-snd
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: UFO: Alien Invasion - ALSA sound support
 "UFO: Alien Invasion" is a game inspired by the XCOM "UFO" series.
 .
 UFO:AI comes with support for several sound systems.  This is an
 alternative sound-support package, which uses ALSA.  Note that using
 an alternative engine requires manual configuration.

