Package: ufoai-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: UFO: Alien Invasion - data-building tool
 "UFO: Alien Invasion" is a game inspired by the XCOM "UFO" series.
 .
 This package includes the map-building tool.

Package: ufoai-server
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: ufoai-data (>= 2.2~~svn)
Description: UFO: Alien Invasion - standalone game server
 "UFO: Alien Invasion" is a game inspired by the XCOM "UFO" series.
 .
 This package includes the standalone game server and the master
 server.  It is only needed if you want to setup a permanent game
 server.

Package: ufoai-data
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ttf-freefont, ttf-dejavu
Recommends: ufoai
Description: Data for UFO: Alien Invasion
 This package contains all the non-optional game data for UFO:AI:
 maps, models, units, sound effects, etc.

Package: ufoai-data-music
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: ufoai
Description: Data for UFO: Alien Invasion
 This package contains the music for UFO:AI.  It is recommended to
 fully experience the game, but not required.
